Package projecttwo

Class Roster

  • java.lang.Object
    • projecttwo.Roster
  • public class Roster
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines a roster consisting of multiple students. The roster can add, delete and remove students. An end user can also request students be printed by some order.
    Author:
    Aryan Jairath, Anis Chihoub
